LEWIS DARTNELL: How
long is the talk?

00:11:31.140 --> 00:11:32.291
How long is this slot?

00:11:32.291 --> 00:11:33.415
BORIS: As much as you want.

00:11:33.415 --> 00:11:33.870
One hour.

