didn't know how

00:35:41.590 --> 00:35:43.770
to have a good time back then.

00:35:43.770 --> 00:35:46.820
It's because they've had
to be sat and cannot smile,

00:35:46.820 --> 00:35:48.906
and someone's jammed a
skull clamp into the back

00:35:48.906 --> 00:35:51.810
of the head.

00:35:51.810 --> 00:35:55.520
